    "Data extracted by GPT-3.5 (Materi-alsBERT) from the full text is approximately 21 times (12 times) than what was collected purely from the abstracts in our previous work for the selected 24 properties.",
    "Additional details about the different stages of the pipelines are discussed in the Methods section, with specific details on data extraction using MaterialsBERT provided in ref. 11.",
    "Polymer-related property data from a journal article can be extracted by leveraging the ability of LLMs to understand the specialized semantics of materials entities discussed in the text.",
